    <p>People who care about <span data-annotate data-ann-color="var(--alert)" data-ann-type="underline">the ethics of the internet</span>.</p>
    <p>People who would like the internet to be a little <span  data-annotate data-ann-color="var(--alert)" data-ann-type="underline">less annoying</span> and a little <span data-annotate data-ann-color="var(--alert)" data-ann-type="underline">more useful</span> in their daily lives.</p>
    <p>People who <span data-annotate data-ann-color="var(--alert)" data-ann-type="underline">want a job</span> that involves making stuff on the internet.</p>
    <p>People who <em>have</em> a job making stuff on the internet, and want to <span data-annotate data-ann-color="var(--alert)" data-ann-type="underline">get better</span> at <span data-annotate data-ann-color="var(--alert)" data-ann-type="underline">making stuff that works for people</span>.</p>
